pregnant or lactating women; and individuals with hearing or visual impairments. Participants who did not complete the proposed tests at the time of collection, did not attend reassessments, were exposed to a new COVID-19 infection, or had a neurological or psychiatric disease unrelated to COVID-19 infection during follow-up were excluded from the study.
